Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.22,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I ask you something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:30.38,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.37,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.91,Default,Blake,0,0,0,, Why’d you join the White Fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.50,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Same reason as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:42.28,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:44.70,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,But why fight when I pass for Human?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.56,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}It’s okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:57.04,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not the first person to ask.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:02.36,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I look just like any other Human girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.09,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}And for years,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.92,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}that’s how I was raised.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.73,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}We lived in Mantle with the other Faunus working the mines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:13.58,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my parents wanted something better for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.40,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}They managed to enroll me in an Atlas prep school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:18.44,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.82,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imagine that - {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:24.42,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1} - a little Faunus girl from Mantle going to the city of dreams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.78,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt like a princess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.52,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I had to follow a set of rules.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.93,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}No bringing friends home, no talking about my parents…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:49.64,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,...and absolutely, under no circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.74,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,was I allowed to change colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:57.07,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,No one could know I was a Faunus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:01:59.82,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Sounds terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.18,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.38,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was confusing at first, but{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:07.03,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}it wasn't hard…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.60,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}especially if it meant being in Atlas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.72,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes, the other girls would say things about the Faunus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:20.36,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}That they were animals, that they were dirty, or they lied, and…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.12,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’d say these things with them…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.18,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}because I felt like I was one of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.45,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:32.00,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}one day, there was a cave-in at the mines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:36.24,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I was at school, when the news broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.80,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Apparently, one of the workers there tripped while handling some agitated Dust crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.14,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,The explosion caused a chain reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:47.84,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,And my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.56,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,...friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:51.92,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,...snickered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.46,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.84,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:11.88,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every inch of me turned blue as I wept.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:18.55,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}And suddenly all the girls that I’d laughed and played with…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.90,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}...were scared of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.45,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:27.64,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.20,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I broke their teeth.
